.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bec412ef1a205eaa9112d63de4e221b6047188b","tid":871411,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"收地幾錢一尺？"},{"pid":"898b2d743b29263c61cec7f9ef41be5120429003","tid":871411,"uid":192068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"以為林奠出到聲?問下自己點對香港先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾貴兩蚊，收番嚟做腥港人家庭團聚有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4093308c0a56a02d59287537c87492f3a4ef454","tid":871411,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4d3de851a31ad092f2c74a8d5743adfd393f1a","tid":871411,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:03:47.000Z","msg":"正體字？"},{"pid":"171e3e20b2747e5c735c908bb7b58e42bdfc264a","tid":871411,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"似個屁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d37d40fdebeb3d5f20ed9f8f902beabbe8e943d","tid":871411,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"係公司笑撚左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8940ec048ab5e7b97d7e38cfd53ab3c0959fc1a","tid":871411,"uid":146805,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6827ded1f882419de1ff80b7c34fee1691f8083b","tid":871411,"uid":184463,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:48:52.000Z","msg":"哈哈見到呢堆人係香港遊行抗議大陸既issue真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同之前連登仔發起聯署要美國介入香港政策一樣咁九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂喂美國人心諗關我撚事咩<br />\n就好似我地心諗惠洲野關我撚事咩<br />\n要死死遠d啦柒頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"智障既係你<br />\n美國依加搞尻中國<br />\n係人都知香港政府就比中共控制<br />\n求美國介入係香港人其中一個逃生希望<br />\n同依加大陸d人落黎<br />\n求under中共既港共政權幫手係2回事<br />\n再畫出腸講句：乜你覺得美國係under中共控制？拎2樣野黎比"},{"pid":"0c80fa44af0d438c6330fa480dfeb94815db9738","tid":871411,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:17:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57410a895a4dd3b254506ea8f0e4ec510b4e4fae","tid":871411,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"攞旅遊簽證攞香港示威係違反逗留條件，入境處唔拉人？"}]}